abstract: Anthony Tommasini reviews performance by cellist Nicolas Alstaedt and pianist Alexander Lonquich at Frick Collection.
lead_paragraph: The cello-piano duo used an intimate setting to their advantage in a program that included Debussy and Beethoven.

headline.main: Review: Nicolas Altstaedt and Alexander Lonquich, in a Stirring Concert at the Frick
headline.print_headline: In the Intimacy of a Frick Salon, Duo Charges Down a Restless Path
